    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135410/extras/0e2f37ee6b3331efbc084abbf809d0f0.avif?t=1749865791\" width=596 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       在《修仙记-消消乐乱斗中》中，你将需要用道具获取整理你神识面板的机会，调整你的神识面板，使得你的神识面板在战斗中可以触发三消效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135410/extras/db866cab7000cecc9b6d6a30f24e6291.poster.avif?t=1749865791\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135410/extras/db866cab7000cecc9b6d6a30f24e6291.webm?t=1749865791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135410/extras/db866cab7000cecc9b6d6a30f24e6291.mp4?t=1749865791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135410/extras/990f8140983d75a603543e5cda4c458e.avif?t=1749865791\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       调整你的装备位置，以便让装备收益最大化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135410/extras/1ea2e8d02fdf94df9b994615f292b585.poster.avif?t=1749865791\" width=600 height=516 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135410/extras/1ea2e8d02fdf94df9b994615f292b585.webm?t=1749865791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135410/extras/1ea2e8d02fdf94df9b994615f292b585.mp4?t=1749865791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135410/extras/f189feaa275fee2f3a3e829e330626a2.avif?t=1749865791\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       选择你接下来的行动，是直面妖魔还是解决事件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135410/extras/b9235f0bb688208b8469a1ae3fcbf4c7.avif?t=1749865791\" width=578 height=434 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135410/extras/6bd31f0e3b6dea565722353ab9f64f40.avif?t=1749865791\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       用你的神识驱动装备，与敌人进行斗法吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135410/extras/ea509542711f9395b839139e07d67289.poster.avif?t=1749865791\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135410/extras/ea509542711f9395b839139e07d67289.webm?t=1749865791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135410/extras/ea509542711f9395b839139e07d67289.mp4?t=1749865791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135410/extras/c9e284ea0ed43fa5a5861207b1fcb715.avif?t=1749865791\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p>",
